ance for deflagration due to the slower rate of 12C(alpha,gamma)16O\nreaction at the lower temperature ~108K, with the caveat that we presently\nneglect the proton-catalyzed reaction sequence of 12C(p,gamma)13O(alpha,p)16O.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2022 06:12:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
